data.description: Live in downtown Edenton in the freshly remodeled  ranch house that is move-in ready. Walk to town, the water and all the shopping located a few streets away.  This 3 bedroom 2 and a half bath ranch home offers all one floor living and a large double garage.  It offers  a traditional floor plan with a large living room and dining room to accomodate friends and family. There is a small bedroom that can serve as an office or suit extra guests.  The bright kitchen leads to the garage where the laundry is located and a huge storage area the entire length of the house. This home is freshly painted, has new counter tops,  new vanities, and recently replaced windows !!  A great place to call home or create a weekend getaway for you.
